headline: Wells Fargo Upgrades Incyte Corporation (INCY) to Overweight From Equal Weight
summary: Incyte Corporation (NASDAQ:INCY) is one of the top most undervalued biotech stocks to buy now. Wells Fargo upgraded Incyte Corporation (NASDAQ:INCY) to Overweight from Equal Weight on August 6, raising the price target to $89 from $67.
